	SUBROUTINE LININD(I)
C
***	MODULE	LININD
***	IDENT	26AP85
C
C Copyright Laser-Scan Laboratories Limited, Cambridge, England.
C
CMOD	Colour set with [ESC] M L not L M       TJH	26-Apr-1985
C	Created					 DM	03-Apr-1985
C
C Set line colour index on a Tektronix 41XX
